# Frontend build

To build the frontend, use the Nix shell (provides Yarn), then run the production build:

1. `cd exemi-frontend`
2. `nix-shell`
3. `yarn build`

Do not assume `npm` or a global Yarn install; use this sequence unless the user specifies otherwise.
